Classic Steakhouse Near Atlanta that‚Äôs perfect for a Date Night - @pampasatl 

Hey Foodies! This is one of our favorite Steakhouses near Atlanta that‚Äôs known for their high end Steaks, extensive Wine list and unique table side presentations. 

@pampasatl is an Argentinian influenced Steakhouse that‚Äôs become a staple in Alpharetta. Cole and I love dining at @pampasatl for a Date Night when we want a classic steakhouse experience. reels.caption:
New Lunch Menu for Buckhead Atlanta Michelin Star Restaurant 

Hey Foodies! We were so excited to hear that the Michelin Star awarded restaurant @brushatl has introduced a phenomenal lunch menu full of sushi rolls, maki rolls and ramen. 

Known for their high quality fish, sushi and sashimi @brushatl adds a great option for lunch in Buckhead Atlanta. Our favorite dishes included the Truffle Duck Shoyu Ramen, Maki Set and A5 Wagyu Katsu Sando. 

The cocktail program at @brushatl is incredible and we love sneaking in a mid day Lychee Martini!

#atlanta #atlantaga #atlantageorgia #atlfoodie #atlantafood #buckheadatlanta

reels.caption:
Fried Chicken and Champagne in Atlanta

Hey Foodies! Are you looking for a fun and unique dining experience in Atlanta? @kitchenkocktailsatl recently opened at @perimetermall and is known for the unique twist in southern classic dishes like fried chicken, lobster tail, shrimp and grits, along with creative waffles. 

@kitchenkocktailsatl is one of if not the ONLY place in Atlanta where you can get a bucket of Fried Chicken and Champagne! How fun is that!

Also, make sure to check out their weekly Happy Hour specials, Monday through Friday from 4PM - 7PM. @kitchenkocktailsatl serves a number of delicious dishes, drinks and mocktails for only $11 which is such a steal!

#atlanta #atlantaga #atlantageorgia #atlantageorgia #atlantafood
